It's about global
thermonuclear war.

00:45:18.000 --> 00:45:20.670
It's about
specifically the movie

00:45:20.670 --> 00:45:21.830
that was done in the '80s.

00:45:21.830 --> 00:45:25.740
So it's very much about what
global thermonuclear war would

00:45:25.740 --> 00:45:28.619
have made sense in the '80s.

00:45:28.619 --> 00:45:30.160
Obviously, the
graphic representation

00:45:30.160 --> 00:45:32.990
of what you see in that game
is a little bit higher end

00:45:32.990 --> 00:45:35.330
than what you would normally
have had in the '80s.

00:45:35.330 --> 00:45:37.621
But they're trying to sort
of not necessarily represent

00:45:37.621 --> 00:45:40.470
things realistically, but sort
